<HEADLINE> Charles Barkley Seeks Screen Role  </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
   SIOUX FALLS, S.D. (AP) -- Sir Charles the thespian?
</P>
<P>
   Former NBA star Charles Barkley, who made a cameo appearance in
the Spike Lee movie ''He Got Game'' in 1998, says he's looking for
roles that will let him create some on-screen mayhem.
</P>
<P>
   ''That's been my ultimate goal, and I've got it narrowed down to
five or 10 scripts,'' Barkley said Sunday before a charity golf
event.
</P>
<P>
