<HEADLINE> U.S. Congratulates Chavez's Win  </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
   WASHINGTON (AP) -- The State Department congratulated President
Hugo Chavez and other winners in Venezuela's national elections and
said they will play a critical role in leading the country through
its political and economic reforms.
</P>
<P>
   Spokesman Philip Reeker said the national electoral council
