Tapani's multi-hit game was the first of his career. After his
second single in the sixth, Bohannon picked him off second. ... The
three-game series marks the Rockies only appearance at Wrigley
Field this season. Colorado is 23-16 at Wrigley, its best road
showing against any team. ... The Cubs called up left-handers
Daniel Garibay and Phil Norton from Triple-A Iowa. ... The last
time the Rockies played at Wrigley on May 5, 1999, they became just
the third team since 1900 to score in every inning of a nine-inning
game.
